{"tid":292063,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"R7000 + HKBN 1000M 既延時問題","createTime":"2017-06-21T05:12:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-27T06:09:15.000Z","uid":113952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0fdbf4829bf4a70a8ee2458e7589b4a773b7890e","tid":292063,"uid":113952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T05:12:54.000Z","msg":"之前router 係ASUS RT N56U, 但用左3年多D就壞左<br />\n(屌你牙石一過保就壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n近排就追左AC68U vs R7000 個post <br />\n最後就揀左R7000,但發覺換完之後,<br />\nWIFI 速度無論係5G定2.4G都慢過以前<br />\n而且就咁用lan 線上網個延時都好高, <br />\n最嚴重情況可以去到上YOUTUBE個PAGE都要近1秒<br />\nRouter setting 就係default setting,已更新FW再reset factory 一次<br />\n但結果係一樣<br />\n有冇人可以救下細路,唔想再買多個router 呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dfbdce879c0f6a4e91ed99c90f74b97210027f4","tid":292063,"uid":115096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T06:08:41.000Z","msg":"換乜router都係一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n機樓問題"},{"pid":"39e83133976724fd8edcdca00fead7f25bea0138","tid":292063,"uid":30821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T06:20:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://speedtest.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fspeedtest.net&d=8eAG5A1w8i1IXExU1jg3cBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=a7bb33b5\" target=\"_blank\">speedtest.net</a><br />\n睇下幾多先啦"},{"pid":"11942e3e1c8502caaebfffa8bc2b8b642ff81907","tid":292063,"uid":30821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T06:20:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://www.speedtest.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.speedtest.net&d=8eAG5A1w8i1IXExU1jg3cBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=858b884e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.speedtest.net</a><br />\n睇下幾多先啦</blockquote>"},{"pid":"94a46ae941c7dfb308887c599cd73e3ff8b213fa","tid":292063,"uid":113952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T12:06:58.000Z","msg":"平時測速係完全冇問題，仲幾靚仔Tim<br />\n但就係有時會好慢<br />\n而家改變左調查方向<br />\n睇下係咪另一部機bt太勁，令到我都lag 埋<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be70608cf63db6cb4b4d6a43438aa4ad4b9ac51c","tid":292063,"uid":18105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T12:10:22.000Z","msg":"會唔會撞左channel ?"},{"pid":"5c4437e7e424bb506e0d0961ba69db674ae4a760","tid":292063,"uid":113952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T12:33:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會撞左channel ?</blockquote><br />\n你指wifi 既channel ?呢個我無check ,因為最大問題係lan 個邊會不定期lag"},{"pid":"ebd52ad65f125e401e21c9727e5a25bd4a05c729","tid":292063,"uid":35971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T13:02:16.000Z","msg":"唔用router係快D？"},{"pid":"c3f48bd30ad03a78e2be7218a65e8c5ec6b74292","tid":292063,"uid":113952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T14:01:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔用router係快D？</blockquote><br />\n係呀，但就試唔到lan 既latency 個問題<br />\n因為有另一部電腦要用上網，唔可能全日直插wan 線測試"},{"pid":"8763c1586388481b23c1525c12088f7604e477c4","tid":292063,"uid":49727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T14:06:59.000Z","msg":"有冇試過ping 去google<br />\n<br />\n開個cmd打 ping -n 300 8.8.8.8 睇下先"},{"pid":"0c5175bf1c7b408eb5bc7a72041747c8051e24f6","tid":292063,"uid":49727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T14:08:26.000Z","msg":"btw 以前用HKBN都係咁<br />\n每5-8秒斷一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申用Cisco 2821"},{"pid":"072d97a1c1618ba93a9160ba307a7935b589aeb2","tid":292063,"uid":113952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T14:13:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇試過ping 去google<br />\n<br />\n開個cmd打 ping -n 300 8.8.8.8 睇下先</blockquote><br />\n個作用係咩，見到時間=14-15ms"},{"pid":"9e5f42bc6bf516b78fb17f1feed11d601448cfbe","tid":292063,"uid":113952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T14:14:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>btw 以前用HKBN都係咁<br />\n每5-8秒斷一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申用Cisco 2821</blockquote><br />\n咁你而家轉左供應商仲有冇同樣問題，假設你仲用緊同一個router"},{"pid":"d85c9f8d93121ed116eccda891de66a5a4791ef6","tid":292063,"uid":49727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T14:18:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇試過ping 去google<br />\n<br />\n開個cmd打 ping -n 300 8.8.8.8 睇下先</blockquote><br />\n個作用係咩，見到時間=14-15ms</blockquote><br />\n睇下有冇一下係爆ping(個數好大) / request timeout咁<br />\n<br />\n我個陣係都係1x ms 咁<br />\n跟住每幾秒有一下request timeout咁"},{"pid":"4d40f9c659578bd01d98a1fca8d87bced8ec12c0","tid":292063,"uid":49727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T14:19:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>btw 以前用HKBN都係咁<br />\n每5-8秒斷一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申用Cisco 2821</blockquote><br />\n咁你而家轉左供應商仲有冇同樣問題，假設你仲用緊同一個router</blockquote><br />\n打上去CS屌左一個星期<br />\n之後同我講機房條線有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3a4b2189163b4445efb0c8187f6334f89afb8d4","tid":292063,"uid":113952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T15:07:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇試過ping 去google<br />\n<br />\n開個cmd打 ping -n 300 8.8.8.8 睇下先</blockquote><br />\n個作用係咩，見到時間=14-15ms</blockquote><br />\n睇下有冇一下係爆ping(個數好大) / request timeout咁<br />\n<br />\n我個陣係都係1x ms 咁<br />\n跟住每幾秒有一下request timeout咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁request timeout 係關機房條線事？"},{"pid":"5debcbec6acaf5accae0a2b2bcfd31eb95a98ded","tid":292063,"uid":32887,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T15:52:07.000Z","msg":"你試下用router to pc果條lan線<br />\n直駁modem試下 一定要同一條<br />\n測試時間長啲<br />\n如果無問題就拎router番去換啦"},{"pid":"603899faa4e1e236bf9c946407930fd4b6cc9574","tid":292063,"uid